title: Astonishing Spider-Man & Wolverine 01-06 (2010, Dgtl-HD, Zon
description: Jason Aaron and Adam Kubert combine forces in this wonderful miniseries about Spider-Man and Wolverine...err, combining forces. Aaron explores the relationship and respect between the two heroes and also has quite a bit of battle as the villains pile up. Kubert's art is dynamic and exciting and the issues are a breeze to read as a result. Thanks to Zone-Empire for these high definiton digital copies, please seed - enjoy! :-)
